00:42:40.253 --> 00:42:49.880
We apply the blood around our house; no weapon formed against us will prosper.

00:42:52.140 --> 00:43:01.357
God has not given us a spirit of fear, but of power, and of love, and of a well-balanced mind.

00:43:01.357 --> 00:43:27.260
Now, Father, the Bible says that Satan has blinded the eyes of the unbeliever, and we take authority over those eyes right now that they would be flooded with light.

00:43:27.260 --> 00:44:01.680
I say in the name of Jesus that they have that 'suddenly' experience with the Holy Spirit right now, that they will no longer be on this path to hell but will be radically born again and ready for the coming of the Lord.

00:44:03.209 --> 00:44:11.079
I thank You that those unsaved loved ones are coming to Jesus right now as we speak.

00:44:11.079 --> 00:44:18.010
If you need Jesus, let me lead you in the sinner's prayer.

00:44:18.010 --> 00:44:25.852
Say this with me: 'Jesus, I believe You're the Son of God.

00:44:33.580 --> 00:44:37.255
