00:44:56.558 --> 00:45:03.946
I want to make You my Lord and personal savior.

00:45:03.946 --> 00:45:09.519
Thank You, Lord, for forgiving me of my sins.

00:45:09.519 --> 00:45:29.599
I love You, Lord, and I'll serve You all the days of my life.

00:45:29.599 --> 00:45:48.349
' That's all you have to do.

00:45:48.359 --> 00:46:11.740
Tell somebody in the comment section if you just gave your heart to Jesus.

