We want to rejoice with you.

00:46:34.711 --> 00:46:48.140
If you don't have a Bible, email us and we'll send you one for free.

00:46:48.140 --> 00:46:58.151
Find a Bible-believing church, get baptized, and keep fanning your flame for Jesus.

