00:47:07.276 --> 00:47:18.880
Reach forth and grab a hold of His garment by faith.

00:47:27.390 --> 00:47:33.960
The woman with the issue of blood said, 'If I could touch the hem of His garment, I'll be made whole.

00:47:33.960 --> 00:47:38.559
' He said, 'Daughter, your faith has made you whole.

