I want Him to say, 'Brandon, I look forward to these days with you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.700
' I used to ask Him about finances, and He said, 'Don't you ever come to My throne asking like that again.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Seek ye first the kingdom.

